<%#
Chainboots iPXE/gPXE from PXELinux via UNDI. Make sure the OS has an iPXE
template associated and the file undionly.kpxe was copied into the TFTP
directory as undionly-ipxe.0 (e.g. from /usr/share/ipxe/undionly.kpxe or
the iPXE project web site). Changes need to be made in the DHCP
configuration to prevent an endless loop to happen.

For more info visit:
http://projects.theforeman.org/projects/foreman/wiki/Fetch_boot_files_via_http_instead_of_TFTP
%>
DEFAULT linux
LABEL linux
KERNEL undionly-ipxe.0
IPAPPEND 2
